content: Is all that stuff built? Or was some of that new things that need to be built? Like where do I really start? I don't want a whole plan. Give me a step or a few that will enable you to get additional context to make your next response to me, on what to do next, without a whole plan, to get to our broad goal, given where we are right now at this moment in time. That's how it needs to work, Plans go to shit really quickly around here...
